title: FUBAR Renamer 2014
description:
FUBAR Renamer 2014
------------------

Here is a new application in the FUBAR series!

This one will destroy all files by giving them random names.

No data will actually be deleted, but all files will be useless because of the random names.


THERE IS NO RECOVERY FROM THIS APPLICATION!

Your computer will be rendered useless, and all your data will be almost unrecoverable.


There is no installation. This application runs when you ask it to.

As always, you will be given 2 warnings when running the application.



/Ubehage
